botPricing.rateMenuMarkdown:
Message cost is variable, so longer messages are more expensive than shorter messages. 
**Send up to 49% more messages** on Poe compared to OpenAI's API. [Learn more](https://help.poe.com/hc/en-us/articles/19945140063636-Poe-Subscriptions-FAQs#h_01JH4A5RK7EHWFQE50P8N508GM)

| Type | Rate |
|------|------|
| Input (text) | 75 points/1k tokens |
| Input (image) | 75 points/1k tokens |
| Bot message | 225 points/message |
| Image generation | Additional costs based on the "Image Generation" section below |
| Chat history | Input rates are applied |
| Chat history cache discount | 50% discount on [cached chat history](https://help.poe.com/hc/en-us/articles/19944206309524-Poe-FAQs#h_01JMDGNARXH8B0MN452N6N7XHP) |
 


 _Image Generation (GPT-Image-1)_
Message cost is variable, based on input tokens, and output size/resolution and quality. [Learn more.](https://help.poe.com/hc/en-us/articles/19944206309524-Poe-FAQs#h_01HCFXCW5CB1DSH6F4WXXYHJFJ)
Image generation inputs are determined by the bot based on the user query.

| Type | Rate |
|------|------|
| Input (text) | 151 points/1k tokens |
| Input (images) | 301 points/1k tokens |
| Output (image) | Based on output image quality and resolution (see 'Output Image Rates' below) |
